(1120, 0, 1, 18247, 20993, 0, '', '', 148, '', 10, '2019-01-21', '14:00', '<p>Trial Rimula R4X 15W-40&nbsp;Forklift MHI (mitsubishi)</p>', '<p>customer want to do trial&nbsp;to seek durabilty/ performance Rimula R4X, setting 750 H as max trial terget.</p>\n<p>based 500 H lab result oil condition it\'s still ok and can be extend more. so today is taking sample for 763 H. for sampling snd to SGS lab</p>', '<p>Submit sample to SGS</p>', ''),
(1121, 0, 1, 7607, 8702, 0, '', '', 148, '', 2, '2019-01-29', '10:00', '<p>Bp Nando. can\'t meet cz he at shift 2</p>\n<p>Bp Agung. can\'t meet cz have meetings</p>\n<p>Bp Ihsan. Purchasing, PE (maintenance), HR for Refrigerator BU.</p>\n<p>Collecting data DVR</p>\n<p>Issue filter blocking at unit Injection M-01 Mitsubishi 850 MG</p>\n<p>They asking lab test for help them for audit data</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>DVR Corena S4 R 46 used for vacuum machine for Compressor refrigerator unit line. we cant&nbsp;collect data cz Bp Ihsan is not in charge for maintenance details.</p>\n<p>Based informastion we get in unit M-01 injection Mitsubishi 850MG have issue filter blocking only this unit, topup frequency 20L/ week. they using Idemitsu since 2004-2017 without flushing. at july 2017 they do total flushing with 12 drum Shell Tellus MX 46.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>taking sampling for unit injection Mitsubishi 850 MG (double oil filter) &amp; 450 MG (Single oil filter).</p>\n<p>other information, user at panasonic more care about periodic oil change, unit they have is relative old.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Production 50 pcs/Hours.</p>\n<p>Other product can we offer Rimula&gt;Generator, Corene&gt;Compressor (2 unit),</p>', '<p>Submit sample to Petrolab.</p>\n<p>in next discussion make sure can meet with bp Nando do interpretation lab result, collect DVR data &amp; detail others oil they need.</p>', ''),
(1122, 0, 1, 7037, 9018, 0, '', '', 148, '', 5, '2019-01-29', '12:00', '<p>Bp Hendra</p>\n<p>Product only 1 SKU Spirax S4 ATF HDX</p>', '<p>they use Hino oil as OEM recomendation start 2016 since hino lunch oil product. before that they use pertamina.</p>\n<p>afer we explain about benefit, promotion for price, he interest for using shell droducts others spirax ATF.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>if they want to make sure about rimula performance at hino R260, we sugesst to trial PO 2 pail and we will monitor performance at unit.</p>\n<p>ODI hino engine oil 15.000 Km &amp; Axle - transmission 30.000 km</p>\n<p>chasis grease &gt; pertamina</p>\n<p>bearing grease &gt; Top 1 lithium complex</p>', '<p>immedietly sending quotation from sales:</p>\n<p>- Rimula R4X 15W-40 existing Hino 10W-40</p>\n<p>- Spirax axle &amp; transmission</p>\n<p>- gadus S1 &amp; S3&nbsp;</p>\n<p>- Recocool HD premium N 25%</p>', ''),
