(1337, 0, 1, 7062, 20182, 0, '', '', 148, '', 11, '2019-03-14', '10:00', '<p>Technical meeting for remonitoring R4X 15W40</p>', '<p>Monitoring dilakukan di total 20 unit 2013-2018 thn<br />detail dari unit akan diinformasikan.<br /><br />teknis pelaksanaan, pengambilan sample pada durasi KM berapa saja dan bagaimana mekanisme pengambilan sample.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 54.0pt;\">Secara tahapan prosedur per-KM nya akan berlaku tahapan sebagai berikut:<br /><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.&nbsp;</span></span>0 KM= Pengcekkan menggunakan<em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"> Boroscope </em>(Lampirkan dokumentasi)<br /><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><u>+</u> 5.000 KM = Sampling 1 + <em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">Dipstick Check</em> + <em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">Top Up</em>, dicatat volumenya<br /><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><u>+</u> 10.000 KM = Pengecekkan menggunakan <em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">Dipstick<br /></em><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><u>+</u> 12.500 KM = Sampling 2 +<em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"> Dipstick Check</em> + <em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">Top Up</em>, dicatat volumenya + <em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">Boroscope<br /></em><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">5.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&