(3635, 0, 1, 4379, 5684, 0, '2019-08-15 14:51:46', '', 169, '', 11, '2019-08-07', '10:00', '<p>Diskusi lanjutan subtitusi oil kompresor</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 1.0in; tab-stops: 1.0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif;\">Hasil visit terakhir pada tanggal 07 Agustus 2019 bahwa PT. Cemindo Gemilang Ciwandan telah melakukan overhaul pada unit kompresor mereka dengan mengganti beberapa part, diantaranya adalah :</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left: 111.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif;\">Bearing</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 111.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif;\">Filter</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 111.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif;\">Oil Cleaning Cooler</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 111.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif;\">Separator</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left: 111.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\';\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">5.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif;\">Seal - seal</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 1.0in; tab-stops: 1.0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Futura Std Medium\',sans-serif;\">Dengan kata lain bahwa unit kompresor yang ada hampir seperti keadaan baru. Pak handhy mengatakan bahwa beliau sangat keberatan apabila proses flushing me